Description: Linked Open Data of Ecology ([LODE][]) is a prototype to integrate the data of ecology by linked data approach. So far the subjects include most of [wildfire][]- [taxonomy][]- biodiversity data of [plants][] and [insects][] in Taiwan. 2011/07/20: Recently we added a new dataset about measurements of DBH(diameters breast height) of tree entities in Nansi forest dynamics plot ([FDP-NS][]).[LODE]: http://ecowlim.tfri.gov.tw/lode[wildfire]: http://ecowlim.tfri.gov.tw/lode/resource/firedb/ForestFireEvent[taxonomy]: http://ecowlim.tfri.gov.tw/lode/page/taibnet/Species[plants]: http://ecowlim.tfri.gov.tw/lode/page/taif/Species[insects]: http://ecowlim.tfri.gov.tw/lode/page/flyhorse/Species[FDP-NS]: http://ecowlim.tfri.gov.tw/lode/resource/fdp/NansiForestDynamicsPlotCensus/01
